object.customQuery:
SELECT distinct import_NonPremTrans.Policy_Key, 
import_NonPremTrans.KeyField1, 
import_NonPremTrans.KeyField2, 
import_NonPremTrans.NoticeType, 
import_NonPremTrans.AgentNo, 
import_NonPremTrans.RecioType, 
import_NonPremTrans.CancelDate, 
import_NonPremTrans.AmountDue, 
import_NonPremTrans.ProcessDate, 
import_NonPremTrans.Pol_Eff_Date 
FROM
 dbo.import_NonPremTrans
 left join dbo.PMS_Policy_NonPremium_Transactions 
 on import_NonPremTrans.Policy_Key = PMS_Policy_NonPremium_Transactions.Policy_Key
 and ltrim(rtrim(import_NonPremTrans.NoticeType)) = PMS_Policy_NonPremium_Transactions.Notice_Type
 and ltrim(rtrim(import_NonPremTrans.ProcessDate)) = PMS_Policy_NonPremium_Transactions.Transaction_Dt
 where PMS_Policy_NonPremium_Transactions.Policy_Key is null
